<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.9">
<l>meyyeṉṟu colluvār collaik karutit</l>
<l rend="indent">toṭuppuṇṭāy veṇṇeyai yeṉṟu</l>
<l>kaiyaip piṭittuk karaiyura lōṭeṉṉaik</l>
<l rend="indent">kāṇavē kaṭṭiṟ ṟilaiyē</l>
<l>ceytaṉa collic cirittaṅ kirukkil</l>
<l rend="indent">cirītarā vuṉkātu tūrum</l>
<l>kaiyil tiriyai yiṭukiṭā yinniṉṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">kārikai yārciri yāmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Thinking the words of those who spoke [to you] to be truth,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “you seized and ate the butter”,</l>
<l>catching [my] hand, did you not tie me</l>
<l rend="indent">to the edge of the mortar so that [they] see me?</l>
<l>Speaking and laughing about those deeds,</l>
<l>if you are far, O Sridhara, your ears with close up.</l>
<l>Please take the thread from my hand</l>
<l>[so that] the women standing here don’t laugh.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
